# Next.js

- Read `AGENTS.md` if present — this repo may use a newer Next.js than your training data.
- Prefer App Router patterns already used in the repo.
- Keep server-only secrets in server components, route handlers, or server actions — never in client bundles.
- Run `make dev` or `npm run dev` to verify locally when UI or routing changes.
